:: Attack Camp {"position":"275,2075","size":"100,100"}
Your //Bloodlust// has no bounds and you charge into the camp without question to kill the next monsters you see. However, you aren't stupid. You understand your distance probably isn't enough from the Orda's presence. You must quietly kill these monsters without drawing attention. 

You hide behind boxes within the camp and analyze your surroundings. You see 3 vampires wandering around in the middle of the camp. You start to plan your moves carefully to quickly and silently assassinate these monsters with ease. Then you look to your left and see another vampire look towards you. Your position becomes //exposed// as the vampire screeches loudly alerting the other vampires to your location.

So much for carefully planning this out. Time to [[fight.|Vampire Fight]]


