:: Final Hunt(Cautious) {"position":"600,2300","size":"100,100"}
You continue walking further down the path to search for more monsters to hunt down. You come to a halt recognizing whooshing sounds. 

"It must be a vampire. But out here?" You questioned. 

You lurk closer towards the vampire and see its all alone out here. Something is wrong here. It doesn't feel right for this vampire to wander here all by itself. 

"This must be a trap. Vampires are territorial creatures and move along in packs and for this specific one wandering out from its group is highly suspicious. Could it be those Orda people? No doubt in my mind." You muttered. 

You lay out your gear and pull out your specialized blow dart that kills on impact. You load the dart into the chamber and quickly blow to drive force shooting it towards the vampire. //Direct hit!// The vampires croaks as it falls to the ground dying from the quick poison spreading through it's body. 

"Gotcha. Now where ar-"

Suddenly two small looking creatures fall upon your position. You quickly leap out of the way from their landing. You see that one creature had a sword over where you were. It's clear you won't be escaping their grasp this time. 

[[Confrontation]]




