As Valeris recounts the story, Nalen's jovial face slowly hardens. "Valeris, this isn't a threat we can ignore. Hell, there might not even be time to call for backup!"

"That's not even the main issue. At his level, most nearby agents would only hinder us."

"Right, forgot most of the Orda's off in Europe. Either way, the trap itself worked like a charm! The only flaw was that we didn't include an offensive component. A turreted barrier, for example, would be more than enough to bring him down, without enough power to self-destruct."

