:: Recruitment {"position":"1400,3500","size":"100,100"}
"What do you mean by a offer?" 

"Please don't kill me. I will lose this fight as my combat abiltiies is below yours. And Valeris here is too busy eating that burger because he loves them so much. He likes to eat things very slowly and once he sets his mind on something, he's going to continue until it's done." Nalen explains. 

"Ah I see. He's a food lover. Now go on with this offer of yours."

"Yes. I propose that you should join us. You are human but you are unlike any human we have ever seen. Your skills show us that a lot and we can use the help we can get."

"But you guys let monsters reign over humans. How is that just?"

"Don't worry about that. I believe we can work something out. What do you say?"

"Hmm.. Alright why not?"

"Hey, what did I miss?" Valeris says. 

"Valeris, meet our new recruit. He will be in good hands under us."

"Nice work Nalen, I'm sorry we got off on the wrong foot here."

"Valeris, don't say another word. You almost left me to die just so you can eat. You need to fix that habit of yours."

Valeris laughs. "I'm sorry Nalen. It's just when I see burgers, I lose my sense of self and go to eat them. They taste ''soooo gooood''."

"Alright you two, can we get a move on now?" You say with impatience. 

The pair guides Silas to follow them back to Orda's HQ. Silas wonders if this offer will be enough to satisfy him. He will have to wait and see. It could be good after all. Just [[maybe.|End Game/Credits]] 


